588
00:23:38,277 --> 00:23:39,944
he was a beach lifeguard
at Martha's Vineyard.

589
00:23:39,946 --> 00:23:41,812
Uh, respectfully,
Mr. Holmes,

590
00:23:41,814 --> 00:23:44,865
