760
00:30:35,648 --> 00:30:37,931
No one ever remembers the
secretary, do they, Donna?

761
00:30:37,933 --> 00:30:39,449
Excuse me, what?

762
00:30:39,451 --> 00:30:41,652
As a career choice,
